OL,3,CWilliam calls for better systems and
OL,4,Cnew approaches to tackle homelessness
OL,6,FThe Prince of Wales is expected to
OL,7,Fdeclare that if "systemic failure"
OL,8,Fcauses homelessness then "systems can
OL,9,Fhelp prevent it" when he marks the
OL,10,Fthird anniversary of his project to
OL,11,Feradicate the issue.
OL,13,FWilliam launched his ambitious five-
OL,14,Fyear Homewards initiative to create a
OL,15,Fblueprint to end homelessness in all
OL,16,Fits forms and has taken stock of the
OL,17,Fprogress so far.
OL,26,@oD@QOUoD@bO]pD@ZOUqD@PO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/11
