PN,30502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1782778699
OL,3,CWilliam calls for better systems and
OL,4,Cnew approaches to tackle homelessness
OL,6,FHazel Detsiny, executive director for
OL,7,Fhomelessness at the prince's Royal
OL,8,FFoundation, said they were now seeing
OL,9,F"green shoots and clear evidence of
OL,10,Fwhat works in practice to prevent
OL,11,Fhomelessness".
OL,13,FIn a speech due to be delivered at an
OL,14,Fevent later on Tuesday to mark the
OL,15,Fthird year of the project, William is
OL,16,Fexpected to say: "Homelessness is not
OL,17,Fan individual failure; it is a
OL,18,Fsystemic failure. And, if systems help
OL,19,Fcreate the problem, then systems can
OL,20,Fhelp prevent it.
OL,26,@qD@AOUsD@MO]xD@ROU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1782778699
OL,3,CWilliam calls for better systems and
OL,4,Cnew approaches to tackle homelessness
OL,6,F"By trialling new approaches,
OL,7,FHomewards is demonstrating how
OL,8,Fprevention can be embedded across
OL,9,Fevery part of our society.
OL,11,F"Proving that our true strength
OL,12,Femerges not in isolation, but in a
OL,13,Fshared purpose that makes us greater
OL,14,Fthan the sum of our parts."
OL,16,FIn 2023, William launched his
OL,17,FHomewards project, which aims to make
OL,18,Fhomelessness "rare, brief and
OL,19,Funrepeated".
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOUvD@[O]zD@NOU{D@KO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/11
