OL,3,CWilliam calls for better systems and
OL,4,Cnew approaches to tackle homelessness
OL,6,FSix Homewards locations were chosen `
OL,7,FNewport, Lambeth, Belfast, Aberdeen,
OL,8,FSheffield and the three neighbouring
OL,9,FDorset towns of Poole, Bournemouth and
OL,10,FChristchurch ` with the aim of
OL,11,Fdelivering bespoke solutions to the
OL,12,Fhomelessness issues in each area.
OL,14,FDuring the past three years, Homewards
OL,15,Fhas invested #1.9 million across the
OL,16,Fsix locations through the Homewards
OL,17,FFund, with another #3.5 million
OL,18,Fleveraged through grants and private
OL,19,Fphilanthropy, organisers have said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1782778699
OL,3,CWilliam calls for better systems and
OL,4,Cnew approaches to tackle homelessness
OL,6,FA further #2.3 million worth of
OL,7,Fsurplus goods has been used to furnish
OL,8,FHomewards homes and 250 people have
OL,9,Fbeen supported into stable employment.
OL,10,FIn Aberdeen alone, 31 people are now
OL,11,Fliving in homes created through the
OL,12,Fprogramme.
OL,14,FThe prince is also expected to say:
OL,15,F"The next two years are about proving
OL,16,Fthat what works in six locations can
OL,17,Fwork across the country."
OL,26,@wD@AOUyD@YO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
