OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1782778699
OL,3,CWilliam calls for better systems and
OL,4,Cnew approaches to tackle homelessness
OL,6,FThe campaign is a major long-term
OL,7,Ffocus for William, who has said
OL,8,Fpreviously how visiting shelters with
OL,9,Fhis late mother Diana, Princess of
OL,10,FWales, when he was a child left a deep
OL,11,Fand lasting impression and inspired
OL,12,Fhis work.
OL,14,FWhen asked what her meetings with the
OL,15,Fprince were like, Ms Detsiny said:
OL,16,F"Punchy, I would say. But the question
OL,17,Fthat the prince always asks me is 'How
OL,18,Fwill we know this has worked at the
OL,19,Fend of five years and how will we know
OL,20,Fit's worked for long-term change?'
OL,26,@xD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30507
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1782778699
OL,3,CWilliam calls for better systems and
OL,4,Cnew approaches to tackle homelessness
OL,6,F"If we start to change the culture, if
OL,7,Fpeople across the whole society think
OL,8,Fdifferently, act differently, work
OL,9,Ftogether, feel optimistic, then that
OL,10,Fwill also be part of that sustainable
OL,11,Flong-term change that will spread to
OL,12,Fother places."
OL,14,FShe went on to say: "We're not
OL,15,Fclaiming that we've got all the
OL,16,Fanswers.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@NO]vD@UOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/11
