PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1782778699
OL,3,CWilliam calls for better systems and
OL,4,Cnew approaches to tackle homelessness
OL,6,F"We're only at the halfway point, but
OL,7,Fwe are now seeing green shoots and
OL,8,Fclear evidence of what works in
OL,9,Fpractice to prevent homelessness and
OL,10,Fhow we can then move on to deliver at
OL,11,Fscale over the next years."
OL,13,FWilliam has travelled to all six of
OL,14,Fthe Homewards locations during the
OL,15,Fpast three years to highlight the aims
OL,16,Fof his project.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@[O]
