OL,3,CWilliam calls for better systems and
OL,4,Cnew approaches to tackle homelessness
OL,6,FCelebrity supporters include former
OL,7,FLioness Fara Williams, TV presenter
OL,8,FGail Porter, Aston Villa footballer
OL,9,FTyrone Mings, Spice Girl Geri Horner,
OL,10,FOpera star Sir Bryn Terfel, and
OL,11,Fbroadcaster Sara Cox.
OL,13,FOpera singer Chelsie Robinson, from
OL,14,FNewport in South Wales, experienced
OL,15,Fhomelessness but was supported back
OL,16,Finto accommodation by Newport city
OL,17,Fcouncil and has become involved in
OL,18,Fhomewards through local working groups.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
